    "description": "Fantastic Fist is a platforming game focused on simultaneous keyboard and mouse controls. While the character can be moved around with the keyboard, the mouse can be used to interact with the environment by punching with a giant fist.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119470/extras/3e78dab377497dc0f78ac25adc4d237d.poster.avif?t=1709182820\" width=632 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119470/extras/3e78dab377497dc0f78ac25adc4d237d.webm?t=1709182820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119470/extras/3e78dab377497dc0f78ac25adc4d237d.mp4?t=1709182820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Featuring:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hidden Collectibles<br><br></li><li>Massive variety in objects you can punch<br><br></li><li>Challenging bonus levels<br><br></li><li>Boxes that have faces on them and sometimes hats</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119470/extras/7640162c91d8ae69ab3447cc38d3c82a.poster.avif?t=1709182820\" width=460 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119470/extras/7640162c91d8ae69ab3447cc38d3c82a.webm?t=1709182820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119470/extras/7640162c91d8ae69ab3447cc38d3c82a.mp4?t=1709182820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This game was solo developed by Chris Siebert. The Art, Music, Levels, Code, and everything else was all made by one person. That said, the game would never be where it is today without the feedback of the playtesters! <br><br>Have fun!",
